# Matek Billiards & Watches | Luxury E-Commerce Suite

![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-1.0.0-gold)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-white)

An ultra-high-end digital storefront designed for **Matek**, specializing in precision billiard cues and luxury horology. This suite features a deep charcoal aesthetic (#1a1a1a) with gold accents (#D4AF37) to evoke a sense of heritage and exclusivity.

---

## 💎 Design Language
- **Typography:** Serif (Playfair Display) for headlines; Sans-serif (Inter) for functional UI.
- **Palette:** - Primary: `Deep Charcoal (#1a1a1a)`
  - Accent: `Gold (#D4AF37)`
  - Text: `Pure White (#FFFFFF) / Slate Gray (#9ca3af)`
- **Experience:** Minimalist transitions, high-quality placeholders, and a mobile-responsive Tailwind architecture.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML5, Tailwind CSS (via CDN)
- **Logic:** Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- **Hosting:** Optimized for GitHub Pages

---

## 📂 Site Architecture
| Filename | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- |
| `index.html` | **Landing Page:** Hero section featuring dual collections. |
| `product.html` | **Product Detail:** Showcase of "The Grand Master" watch ($4,500). |
| `cart.html` | **Shopping Cart:** Minimalist item summary and subtotaling. |
| `checkout.html` | **Secure Checkout:** Elegant payment and shipping portal. |
| `confirmation.html` | **Order Success:** Post-purchase "Luxury Seal" confirmation. |
| `login.html` | **Identity Portal:** Gateway for customers and system creators. |
| `dashboard.html` | **Creator Dashboard:** Private management and system overview. |

