## 🚀 Deployment Instructions
1. Clone this repository.
2. Ensure all 7 `.html` files are in the root directory.
3. Navigate to **GitHub Settings > Pages**.
4. Select the `main` branch as the source.
5. Your luxury suite will be live at `https://<your-username>.github.io/<repo-name>/`.

